'''咪俚语'''是一种在中国[[云南省|云南省]][[景东彝族自治县|景东彝族自治县]](在安定乡和文龙乡<ref name="AsiaHarvest">{{Cite web |title=China |url=http://asiaharvest.org/index.php/people-group-profiles/china/ |url-status=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130801062653/http://asiaharvest.org/index.php/people-group-profiles/china/ |archive-date=2013-08-01 |access-date=2013-07-19 |website=Asia Harvest }}</ref>)、[[云县|云县]]、[[镇沅彝族哈尼族拉祜族自治县|镇沅彝族哈尼族拉祜族自治县]]和[[新平彝族傣族自治县|新平彝族傣族自治县]]使用的[[彝语支|彝语支]][[彝语中部方言|彝语中部方言]]。<ref name="Yang2011">Yang, Cathryn. 2011. ''Assessment of the Lolo languages: Current understanding and recommended next steps''. m.s.</ref>


